<h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>

<div class="content-box">
    <h3>Who can benefit from Helping Hands?</h3>
    <p>Anyone in need of assistance, whether it be food, shelter, or educational support, is welcome to apply for help through our platform.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-box">
    <h3>How do I register as a beneficiary?</h3>
    <p>Visit the <a href="/Beneficiary/Register">Beneficiary Registration</a> page and fill out the form with your details to get started.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-box">
    <h3>How can I volunteer?</h3>
    <p>We welcome individuals with a passion for helping others! Head to the <a href="/Volunteer/Register">Volunteer Registration</a> page to sign up.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-box">
    <h3>How is my donation used?</h3>
    <p>Donations are used to fund our various programs, including food distribution, education initiatives, and disaster relief. We ensure complete transparency with fund allocation.</p>
</div>
